thread.title: Marcia S Lanting
thread.title_full: SimplyOz.com reviewed by Marcia S Lanting

author: Marcia S Lanting
title: Marcia S Lanting
text: WOW! We ordered Tim Tam cookies one day and three days later they arrived in perfect condition. We were lucky enough to spend a month in Australia last year. Missed the white chocolate Tim Tams. Sent some to my friend undergoing chemo to share great memories. Will be ordering again! Thanks!
